channel.title: FTB whitelist
channel.description:
A whitelist has been introduced for the FTB server, I've listened to everyones input on this matter and decided this is the best course of action to ensure the stability of our server. If you would like to be added to the whitelist please PM a staff member, and the procedure will begin. We'll try and deal with the application ASAP, when applying please ensure you include any information you deem relevant (like: your mc name, any past information etc).
